bibl.title: A Stamp with a Representation of Eros Riding a Dolphin from Tell Atrib.
bibl.note: Inv. TA 1990/12p. Relief stamp for votive bread found in 1990 in the masonry of the wall of room 138 in the southern end of the JJ sector. First half of the second century B.C. or slightly earlier.
SZCZEPKOWSKA Joanna Katarzyna, A Stamp with a Representation of Eros Riding a Dolphin from Tell Atrib.
